<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-2050] Add predictor to LZW filter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2050</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;According to the PDF spec &quot;LZW and Flate Predictor Functions&quot;, both can have post processing with predictors. It is implemented for Flate but not for LZW. I am adding this by using the existing code from the Flate filter, which I will be moving into a helper class.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;While looking at the Flate filter, I noticed that its footprint is higher than needed, i.e. there is too much buffering. I will test this separately and commit only if I can measure an improvement.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
